    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a mechanically sound example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The 3.2L inline-six pulls hard to its 8,000 RPM redline, benefiting from a recent VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement for long-term high-performance reliability. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity has been proactively addressed with rear subframe reinforcement, mitigating the common floor pan fatigue associated with this generation. Suspension kinematics remain sharp with refreshed bushings and dampers. While the aesthetic shows honest patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the powertrain and structural components are dialed in for the purist seeking an engaging, analog driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Used vehicle in good condition. Clean title. Regular maintenance records available. Interior is clean. Mechanically sound. Test drives welcome for serious buyers.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
